{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.15\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">大卫的诗。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">得居圣山者的品行</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.15.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>耶和华啊，谁能寄居你的帐幕？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">谁能居住你的圣山？</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.15.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>就是行为正直、做事公义、</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">心里说实话的人。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.15.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>他不以舌头谗害人，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">不恶待朋友，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">也不随伙毁谤邻舍。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.15.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>他眼中藐视匪类，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">却尊重那敬畏耶和华的人。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">他发了誓，虽然自己吃亏也不更改。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.15.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>他不放债取利，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">不受贿赂以害无辜。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\">做这些事的人必永不动摇。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}